T02D3146:170a-1: stu ti aa nu sham sa /
T02D3146:170a-4: 'di dag sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
T02D3146:170a-5: yang dag yon tan rgya chen yin //
T02D3146:170a-6: de dag lan cig brjod pas kyang //
T02D3146:170a-7: gang phyir sngags pas thams cad 'grub //
T02D3146:170a-8: bstod ba'i rgyal po 'di dag gis //
T02D3146:170a-9: de bzhin gshegs pa mnyes byed de bskal par gnas dang lhag pa dang //
T02D3146:170a-10: dngos grub rgya chen ster bar gsungs //
T02D3146:170a-11: blta bas chog mi shes pa yi //
T02D3146:170a-12: bdag nyid sku yang ston par mdzad //
T02D3146:170a-13: rnam par snang mdzad mgon po che //
T02D3146:170a-14: mi bskyod pa dang rin chen 'byung //
T02D3146:170a-15: dag pa'i rgyal ba snang mtha' yas //
T02D3146:170a-16: don yod grub rgyal thams cad kyis //
T02D3146:170a-17: gser 'gyur dang ni bcud kyis len //
T02D3146:170a-18: de nyid mchog kyang rab tu sbyin //
T02D3146:170a-19: dngos grub dgar gyur rnams yangs shing //
T02D3146:170a-20: ma lus don rnams phun tshogs pa //
T02D3146:170a-21: bsam pa kun yang rdzogs byed pa'i //
T02D3146:170a-22: yid la sems pa ster bar mdzad //
T02D3146:170a-23: shes rab che dang stobs shugs rnams //
T02D3146:170a-24: mchog tu dge ba snang bar mdzad //
T02D3146:170a-25: ces pa bstod pa'i phan yon dang bcas pa 'di
T02D3146:170a-26: nyid ni rnal 'byor chen po'i rgyud rdo rje'i dkyil
T02D3146:170a-27: 'khor gyi rgyan las gsungs pa yin no //
